               <p>A second count for feloniously stealing the same coffee, the property of persons unknown.</p>
               <p>Mr. Silvester of council for the prosecution opened the case as follows:</p>
               <p>May it please your Lordship, and you Gentlemen of the Jury,</p>
               <p>This is an indictment against the four prisoners at the bar, 
               <persName id="t17831029-5-person160">
