            , and Edward Hudson, for stealing on the 6th of September last, a quantity of coffee from on board the Arend op Zee which was a Dutch prize to his Majesty's ships, Hercules, Leander, Dolphin, and Nemesis, and which was then laying on the <placeName id="t17831029-5-crimeloc30">river of Thames</placeName>
